1-0.query:
SELECT MIN(mc.note) AS production_note, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title, MIN(t.production_year) AS movie_year
 FROM random_company_type_4 AS ct,
 random_info_type_4 AS it,
 random_movie_companies_4 AS mc,
 random_movie_info_idx_4 AS mi_idx,
 random_title_4 AS t
 WHERE ct.id = mc.company_type_id
 AND t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
 AND ct.kind = '@param0'
 AND it.info = '@param1'
 AND mc.note NOT LIKE '@param2'
 AND (mc.note LIKE '@param3' OR mc.note LIKE '@param4');
